Are you ready to Manifest?

Do you want change in your life?

Have you been looking for like-minded supportive people you can share with?

Do you want to be inspired?


Hi Everyone...

I am back from my manifested trip to Australia and I am really looking forward to getting back into the swing of things with all of you...

In our new Holistic Center( another amazing recent manifested dream)...

It's an exciting time to get pumped, motivated, enthusiastic, passionate about living your dreams...They can and do happen...

The energy is ripe and there is no better time than the present...

 

This will be our first meeting of the New Year and we will be setting the stage and foundation for the upcoming months...

There will be LOA teachings, an open forum, networking opportunities(6:30-7pm),  and a raffle for a giveaway for those who come... It's a good opportunity to shift your life and Co-create what you are wanting... Come with questions, ideas, challenges...

 

Looking forward to seeing you all... Many Blessings Magnificent Manifestors!!!!!!

Nicole
